{"word":"ἐπικουρία","slug":"ἐπικουρία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπικουρία</b></el> <el>(ἐπικουρία, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐπικουρέω'><el>ἐπικουρέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>aid, succour</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an auxiliary</i> or <i>mercenary force</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}